        <h3>How to Check BCom (Year-wise) Result 2024 officially?</h3>
        <p>While the informational sites are for news, the **University Official Portal** is for marks. To check officially:</p>
        <p>
            1. Visit the **official result portal of your university** (e.g., mu.ac.in or result.uniraj.ac.in).<br>
            2. Click on the 'Undergraduate (UG) Results' section on the homepage dashboard.<br>
            3. Choose your specific year-link (e.g., B.Com Part-I Exam 2024 / B.Com Year 3 Result).<br>
            4. Enter your **University Roll Number** (accurately as on the hall ticket).<br>
            5. Select your 'Course Category' (B.Com General / B.Com Honors) and click 'Proceed'.<br>
            6. View your 'Detailed Mark Report' showing subject-wise marks and passing status.<br>
